Anh Duong https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Anh_Duong 0 Anh Duong (born 25 October 1960) is a French-American artist, actress, and model. She is known for her self-portraits, which she has compared to a visual diary, as well as portraits of significant art collectors and influencers.
